query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('stackoverflow')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('.net',
'clojure',
'cookies',
'google-cloud-firestore',
'google-maps-api-3',
'hive',
'modal-dialog',
'network-programming',
'stream',
'xcode');
